title: What’s behind this year’s frightening flu season?
description: This flu season has been among the worst in more than a decade — about as bad as the 2009 season, when the new swine flu strain was spreading madly worldwide. Part of the problem? We don’t have a very good vaccine.
seo_title: Graphics show the worst flu season in more than a decade
author: Erin Allday and Emma O'Neill
twitter_text: What’s behind this year’s frightening flu season?
